      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Spongy Oasis",
        "Client": "Desert Inventor",
        "Description": "You know how Royal Ludroth hide\r\nis all spongey and absorbs lots of\r\nwater, right? If we get a bunch of it,\r\nthen desert farmers will never have\r\nto worry about watering their crops\r\never again! I. AM. A. GENIUS!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Royal Ludroth",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Des \u00E9ponges \u00E0 gogo",
        "Client": "Inventeur du d\u00E9sert",
        "Description": "Tu sais que la peau du Ludroth\r\nroyal peut absorber beaucoup\r\nd\u0027eau, n\u0027est-ce pas ? Si on en\r\navait assez, les fermiers du\r\nd\u00E9sert n\u0027auraient plus \u00E0 se\r\nsoucier de la s\u00E9cheresse !\r\nUne id\u00E9e de g\u00E9nie, hein ?!",
        "Target": "Chasser un Ludroth royal",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Oasi di spugna",
        "Client": "Inventore del deserto",
        "Description": "Sai che la pelle dei Ludroth\r\nreali \u00E8 spugnosa e assorbe\r\nmolta acqua, no?\r\nProcurandocene parecchia,\r\ni contadini del deserto non\r\ndovranno mai pi\u00F9 preoccuparsi\r\ndi irrigare i campi! GENIALE!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Ludroth reale",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Schwammige Oase",
        "Client": "W\u00FCstenerfinder",
        "Description": "Die Lederhaut des K\u00F6nigs-\r\nLudroth ist wie ein Schwamm\r\nund absorbiert Wasser. Wenn\r\nwir ein paar h\u00E4tten, k\u00F6nnten\r\ndie Bauern in der W\u00FCste ihre\r\nFelder viel leichter bew\u00E4s-\r\nsern. ICH BIN EIN GENIE!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen K\u00F6nigs-Ludroth.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Oasis esponjoso",
        "Client": "Inventor del desierto",
        "Description": "\u00BFSabes que la piel de Ludroth\r\nReal retiene fluidos de\r\nmaravilla? Si obtenemos unas\r\ncuantas, \u00A1los granjeros del\r\ndesierto no volver\u00EDan a tener\r\nproblemas con la irrigaci\u00F3n!\r\n\u00A1Soy un genio!",
